If you are in need of extra support, such as requiring electricity for medical equipment, you can call us on 105 where our teams will be on hand to help.

For information on welfare provisions and latest updates on our response to the weather, please click here.

Thank you for your ongoing patience.
Faults.name: HS2 Area
